{"tid":1431483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(立場新聞) 反對成立大台 ，泛民割蓆只會自毀","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T05:15:02.000Z","uid":134071,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9541ebc208e14d119ebe03b2245d964be6ae6638","tid":1431483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/反對成立大台-回應-給抗爭者的公開信/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%B0-%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E7%B5%A6%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1%2F&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rD11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=4e29f5db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%8F%B0-%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89-%E7%B5%A6%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E4%BF%A1%2F&h=4424a1e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/反對成立大台-回應-給抗爭者的公開信/</a><br />\n<br />\n反對成立大台 &mdash; 回應「給抗爭者的公開信」<br />\n讀者投稿 2019/8/8 &mdash; 10:48<br />\n<br />\n【文： James Wong 】<br />\n<br />\n致 一對平凡的香港夫婦︰<br />\n<br />\n1) 「時代革命」絕不是港獨語句。 泛民會議召集人毛孟靜也指出「光復香港 時代革命」絕不是港獨語句。其實中共一早已定性「反修例」抗爭是港獨運動， 但很多外國政客依然支持， 因為外國政客們也明白「反修例」抗爭絕不是港獨運動。（相反， 西班牙加泰獨立運動，開宗明義要求獨立，便近乎沒有外國支持。）只要繼續讓外國政客明白「反修例」抗爭絕不是港獨運動，「反修例」抗爭便會繼續有外國支持，中共亦不敢像對藏獨疆獨那麼樣打壓。（畢竟， 如果香港「一國兩制」破滅，會大大損害中國經濟。）<br />\n<br />\n2) 從現在「反修例」抗爭看來，示威者十分懂得靈活變通。就算沒有大台，示威者都會懂得跟據民意和形勢而靈活應變。林鄭視民意如無物，但示威者不是。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3) 泛民不見得比示威者更能掌握民意。泛民以往跟街頭示威者「割蓆」，結果在選舉節節敗退，令九龍西淪為建制派票倉。（毛孟靜也表示往日的「割蓆」是錯誤。）</strong><br />\n<br />\n4) 以往，泛民和本土派也因大台問題而爭鬥不斷，結果所有反對派也一事無成。 現在，反對派各個派別也放棄大台，合作關係反而更好。<br />\n<br />\n平凡的香港人 James Wong 上<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月8日"},{"pid":"675a719f494643caa6e7b2fb359a56719dec4bc3","tid":1431483,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:09:46.000Z","msg":"呢篇同《<strong>給抗爭者的公開信：你們願意交棒給大台嗎？</strong>》一樣, <strong>只係讀者投稿, </strong><br />\n邊個都投得, (鬼都投得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"5be3ec5a4515dda575433f43db8185687dd07906","tid":1431483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:11:01.000Z","msg":"(立場新聞) 全面反駁《給抗爭者的公開信：你們願意交棒給大台嗎？》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1431194/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1431194/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n極懷疑立場《給抗爭者的公開信：你們願意交棒給大台嗎？》 係鬼寫！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1429546/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1429546/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6d234365578dbd094f4dcb64b3b98168d739ee6a","tid":1431483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"3c41ce465f59ad9697562ff2927f35f6a2477a6f","tid":1431483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:24:53.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"7c1d272373d7819c779cbda29b38d65df49ee9db","tid":1431483,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38629af615e8ba457167220a7f7b4e67f28995ed","tid":1431483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:34:31.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"03bb6831947780ec05c752f99d0470ec63b8839e","tid":1431483,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"ff2d0af7f8d291edd95db33cf2f74f89791bfaa2","tid":1431483,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭政權唯一依靠 ─ 黑警 ─ 崩潰前夕，勝利近在咫尺之時，<br />\n你同我講停止勇武，和理非唱歌鳩行，建大台？<br />\n你無撚嘢呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t9M3Yak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft9M3Yak.jpg&h=ba4d70ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O51Lr3O.jpg\" data-thumbnail